        <div class="component-inner">



                <div class="info ">

        

        <div class="text base-text " data-os-animation="fadeIn" data-os-animation-delay="0s">
            <p class="MsoNormal intro sm">Haldimand County has 7 elected officials – 1 mayor and 6 councillors – who serve a 4-year term. Each member has one vote on items before Council.</p>
<h2 class="MsoNormal">Council members</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="#mayor" data-anchor="#mayor">Mayor Shelley Ann Bentley</a></li>
<li><a href="#ward-1" data-anchor="#ward-1">Councillor Debera McKeen</a></li>
